latestIgtvVideos.title: Ocean Art 🌊
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
While the pandamic is still on and we need choose wisely before stepping outside.
So, I decided use this time to learn something new 🤷‍♀️ at the comfort of my home 🏠 

Thanks to #JioFiber that made it easier for me to learn resin art. 

Painting always brings me joy and helps me explore new horizons! So here I am taking 
#30DaysAtHomeChallenge 

Follow @kumar_resin_works if you want to use this time at home to learn something new and let your creative juices flow! 🦋
